strings.Value: "Ah, rest at last! Finally I can sit and read quietly!"
"No. No reading. Fetch water. Or you can read and stay hungry."
"Why don't you pull your nose out of your books and talk to one of your companions, Jubilost? An evening by the fire is the best time for conversation."
